    "answer_id" : 2417584,
    "question_id" : 2417485,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 2.5",
    "body" : "<p>Although it doesn't make much difference on the way in, it does on the way back.</p>\n\n<p>Sure you can use either '/' or '\\' in new File(String path), but File.getPath() will only give you one of them.</p>\n"
  }, {
    "comments" : [ {
      "owner" : {
