    "question_id" : 2417485,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<p>If you are using Java 7, checkout <a href=\"http://docs.oracle.com/javase/7/docs/api/java/nio/file/Path.html#resolve(java.nio.file.Path)\" rel=\"nofollow\">Path.resolve()</a> and <a href=\"http://docs.oracle.com/javase/7/docs/api/java/nio/file/Paths.html#get(java.lang.String,%20java.lang.String...)\" rel=\"nofollow\">Paths.get()</a>.</p>\n"
