    "question_id" : 2417485,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<p>As the gentlemen described the difference with variant details.</p>\n\n<p>I would like to recommend the use of the <a href=\"http://commons.apache.org/proper/commons-io/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Apache Commons io</a> api, class <code><a href=\"http://commons.apache.org/proper/commons-io/apidocs/org/apache/commons/io/FilenameUtils.html\" rel=\"nofollow\">FilenameUtils</a></code> when dealing with files in a program with the possibility of deploying on multiple OSs.</p>\n"
  }, {
