      "body" : "In this line <code>getClass().getClassLoader().getResourceAsStream(&quot;path\\to\\res&zwnj;&#8203;ource&quot;);</code>, there are a tabulation (<code>\\t</code>) and a carriage return (<code>\\r</code>)."
